# dena Weekly Report Agent

An autonomous agent that collects current articles about the German Energy Agency (dena) on a weekly basis and generates a structured report.

## Stack

- **Python 3.11+**
- **LangChain + OpenAI (GPT-4o-mini)** – Report generation
- **NewsAPI** – Current articles (last 7 days)

## Setup

```bash
# 1. Clone repository
git clone <repo-url>
cd dena-agent

# 2. Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Windows: venv\Scripts\activate

# 3. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 4. Set up API keys
# Create .env file with your API keys:
# NEWSAPI_KEY=your_key_here
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your_key_here
```

## Get API Keys

- **NewsAPI:** https://newsapi.org (free, 100 requests/day)
- **OpenAI:** https://platform.openai.com/api-keys

## Usage

### Run the agent

```bash
# Default (Energy transition)
python main.py

# Specific industry
python main.py --industry energiewende
python main.py --industry gebaeude
python main.py --industry energie_erzeugen
python main.py --industry digitalisierung
python main.py --industry wirtschaft
```

### Available industries

| Key | Topic |
|-----|-------|
| `energiewende` | dena & Energy transition (default) |
| `gebaeude` | Buildings & retrofit spaces |
| `energie_erzeugen` | Generate & distribute energy |
| `digitalisierung` | Digitalization & Innovation |
| `wirtschaft` | Transform economy |

### Output

Reports are saved automatically to `reports/` as Markdown files: `reports/<topic>_report_YYYY-MM-DD.md`

### Add a new industry

Edit `industries.yaml` and add a new entry with the keys:
`label`, `newsapi_query`, `rss_keywords`, `rss_keyword_filter`, `report_topic`

## Run

```bash
python main.py
```

The report will be saved to `reports/dena_report_YYYY-MM-DD.md`.

## Workflow

```
Start → NewsAPI (last 7 days) → Format articles → OpenAI Report → Save as .md
```

## Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    dena Report Agent                     │
│                      main.py                            │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                           │
              ┌────────────▼────────────┐
              │   industries.yaml       │
              │   (industry config)     │
              └────────────┬────────────┘
                           │
           ┌───────────────┼───────────────┐
           │                               │
┌──────────▼──────────┐       ┌────────────▼────────────┐
│   Tool 1: NewsAPI   │       │ Tool 2: Tagesschau RSS   │
│  newsapi.org/v2/    │       │ tagesschau.de/xml/rss2/  │
│  - keyword query    │       │ - keyword filter         │
│  - last 7 days      │       │ - no API key required    │
│  - retry logic      │       │ - public feed            │
└──────────┬──────────┘       └────────────┬────────────┘
           │                               │
           └───────────────┬───────────────┘
                           │
              ┌────────────▼────────────┐
              │  merge_and_deduplicate  │
              │  format_for_prompt      │
              └────────────┬────────────┘
                           │
              ┌────────────▼────────────┐
              │  LangChain + GPT-4o-mini│
              │  - SystemMessage        │
              │  - structured prompt    │
              │  - retry logic          │
              └────────────┬────────────┘
                           │
              ┌────────────▼────────────┐
              │  reports/<topic>_       │
              │  report_YYYY-MM-DD.md   │
              └─────────────────────────┘
```

## Project Structure

```
dena-agent/
├── main.py           # Main agent
├── requirements.txt
├── .env              # Do not commit!
├── reports/          # Generated reports
├── docs/
│   └── stories.md    # Agile planning
├── skills/
│   └── report_generation.md
└── AGENTS.md
```
